                <note type="updated" update="title" import="tengyur-data-1683-1783_PH_new_v2.4.xml" date-time="2021-11-02T13:27:55.711Z" user="admin">In the promise of composition, the author states, “I will explain the stages of the Dharma Empowerment that gather together the essence of the Unexcelled Yoga
